The,TM,Forum,Loyalty,Management,API,is,a,useful,tool,for,developing,loyalty,program,specifications,and,monitoring,loyalty,account,activities,It,supports,the,entire,spectrum,of,loyalty,management,activities,right,from,the,registration,of,loyalty,program,member,accounts,and,definition,of,the,applicable,terms,and,conditions,to,the,tracking,of,the,products,and,balances,associated,with,the,loyalty,accounts,The,RESTful,API,sends,requests,in,URI,Query,String,CRUD,and,JSON,formats,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format,The,API,is,currently,a,beta,release